markdownRemark.html: A quiz app to showcase Polymer web technology & Material Design @ Google IO 2014. In collaboration with @zachgibson & the Polymer engineering team, I worked on all aspects of design from project ideation, visual/interaction design to animation. Topeka is open sourced on github. See project announcement on Google Blog.
